sources.title: Danny. Legend. God. | Full Movie | Action Crime | Dimo Alexiev
sources.description:
A British journalist travels to Bulgaria to film a crime documentary about the meteoric rise of a local businessman, but the project’s subject has different plans, in this thrilling and chaotic comedy about a larger-than-life personality.
2020.  Stars: Dimo Alexiev, Kate Nichols, James Ryan Babson
